    "He witnessed the reopening of the DAI in 1953, but died before he could deliver an address commemorating its 125th founding.": [],
    "His Heidelberg students included <a href=\"/brendelo\">Otto J. Brendel</a> and at the DAI, <a href=\"/schefoldk\">Karl Schefold</a>.": [],
